-- Without LIMIT 1\nEXPLAIN SELECT * FROM `user` WHERE `username` = 'nick';\n+----+-------------+-------+-------+---------------+---------+---------+-------+------+-------+\n| id | select_type | table | type  | possible_keys | key     | key_len | ref   | rows | Extra |\n+----+-------------+-------+-------+---------------+---------+---------+-------+------+-------+\n| 1  | SIMPLE      | user  | const | PRIMARY,username | username | 16      | const | 1    | NULL  |\n+----+-------------+-------+-------+---------------+---------+---------+-------+------+-------+\n\n-- With LIMIT 1\nEXPLAIN SELECT * FROM `user` WHERE `username` = 'nick' LIMIT 1;\n+----+-------------+-------+-------+---------------+---------+---------+-------+------+-------+\n| id | select_type | table | type  | possible_keys | key     | key_len | ref   | rows | Extra |\n+----+-------------+-------+-------+---------------+---------+---------+-------+------+-------+\n| 1  | SIMPLE      | user  | const | PRIMARY,username | username | 16      | const | 1    | NULL  |\n+----+-------------+-------+-------+---------------+---------+---------+-------+------+-------+